name: Kanu
description:
Will you be able to look into your soul and illuminate all its dark corners without fear or doubt? Kanu is a fire that can destroy any darkness and any shadow. Phoenix.  Helps to look into yourself and return without gaining or losing anything. Will you be able to light the torch and dispel the darkness, not knowing what is in the dark and despite the consequences? Helps in the implementation of any creative ideas. Rune of Incarnation. 

The purchase of this nft opens access to additional materials: a link to a folder (yandexdisk) with sketches, alternative designs and my article about the rune, as well as a 100% discount on a physical object. Object description: Rune of renewed Clarity. A unique stone with the Kanu rune. The design is based on this image.
